{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/blood-pressure-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/blood-pressure-driving","title":"Blood pressure problems and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T12:53:43+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2234","business_proposition":false,"description":"You may need to tell DVLA if you have high or low blood pressure - download form to inform DVLA","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You may need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you have high or low blood pressure, depending on what type of driving licence you hold.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car and motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>If you hold a car or motorcycle licence, you don&rsquo;t need to tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about your medical condition.</p>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach and lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>Fill in BP1 questionnaire and send to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_185835.pdf\" title=\"Download ‘BP1 - Confidential medical information’(PDF, 247KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘BP1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 247KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":""},"tags":[],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:10:22+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:13:59+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/giving-up-your-driving-licence.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/giving-up-your-driving-licence","title":"Surrendering your driving licence","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:09:58+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:11:37+00:00"}]}